  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another increase from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Postmaster General Ranjith Ariyaratne said that the revised postal rates will be implemented from tomorrow (15).",
        "Accordingly, the normal postage rate from Rs 15 has been revised to Rs 50.",
        "Also, the postal concession fee for charitable organizations has also been revised. The fee, which was Rs 12 per 20 grams, has been revised to Rs 30. (a)"
      ],
